channel.title: Help me find some lost GIFs
channel.description:
Few weeks ago i accidentally formatted my hard drive in mac (stupid, stupid, stupid machine!), and one of things i miss is my collection of gifs and pics. I would be very happy if someone has some of these: (ones i remember)
-"gangsta" looking black man drives his car near another car, looks inside, and there's a serious looking cat inside. Gangsta laughs and drives away, then animation is reversed, he drives back to cat, looks at it, and laughs again - loop.
-Sniper looks through the scope, then you see soccer field, then back to sniper, he fires a bullet, and one of the players falls down.
-I'm sure it's someones signature on this forum. Kitten is in cup, someones palm covers it, kitten hides, palm goes away, kitten looks out, palm covers it again etc.
